The proposed model did not capture the under-reporting of cases in the Mato Grosso do Sul. Similar behavior occurred for under-reporting deaths in the states of Acre and Mato Grosso do Sul. These are the cases in which under-reporting cannot be observed (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
